Package com.six.timapi.constants

Enum Class TransactionType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TransactionType>
com.six.timapi.constants.TransactionType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TransactionType>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum TransactionType extends Enum<TransactionType>

Defines the type of transaction.

Used as attribute to classify the transaction in the invalid input: '<'sixml:TrxDetail> field.

The following values are valid:

Guides: retail, petrol, unattended, advancedRetail, banking, hospitality, valueAddedServices.
